Question: Why is the man taking pictures of the buses?

Reference Answer: picture

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/110138.jpg

Original program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='man')
IMAGE0=CROP_BELOW(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='buses')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX1)
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'taking pictures' if {ANSWER0} > 0 else 'no reason'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER1)
```
